# Rickbase client-side environment variables.
# Copy this file to `.env.local` and fill in your own values.
#
# WARNING: Vite inlines every VITE_* variable into the public JS bundle.
# Anything you put here is visible to anyone who loads the site, so only
# use keys that are safe to expose to browsers (e.g. public RPC URLs,
# BaseScan free-tier API keys that are rate-limited per IP).

# BaseScan / Etherscan V2 API key.
#
# Used for:
#   - Wallet analytics on HomePage (account txlist/txlistinternal/tokentx)
#   - Contract verification (verifysourcecode + checkverifystatus) on Base Mainnet
#
# Endpoint: https://api.etherscan.io/v2/api?chainid=8453
#
# Note: Etherscan's FREE tier does NOT cover Base Mainnet writes (verification).
# Reads may fall back to the keyless Blockscout API, but verification requires
# an Etherscan key whose plan includes Base.
#
# Create / upgrade a key at: https://basescan.org/myapikey
VITE_BASESCAN_API_KEY=
